title: Amazing value
text:
I wasn't sure whether these were worth it or not, given the cost compared to the original branded filters.

I can happily report that these are a great value and work every bit as good as the original. If you are on the fence worrying whether these are worth it- I can assure you they are.

title: WOW im impressed !!!!!!
text:
im excited to see how the coffee comes out i got 2 mason jars too so i ordered a 2nd one of these so i'll always have 2 in the fridge for the summer

UPDATE: my first cup was a bit strong i added way too much coffee i guess but i watered it down with plenty of ice and half and half - a little cinnamon and vanilla - i ordered the 2nd filter and it will be here soon and i plan to have iced coffee all summer ... definitely cutting down on the amount of coffee though !!!!!
